Name: ureterolithiasis
Definition: An ovarian disease that is characterized by irregular or absent ovulation.

Name: pyoureter
Definition: A chronic purulent otitis media which involves perforation in the attic region (pars flaccida of the tympanic membrane) or at the posterosuperior margin

Name: ureterocele
Definition: A ureteral disease that is characterized_as a congenital anomaly in which the distal end of the ureter swells as it enters the bladder.

Name: vesicoureteral reflux
Definition: A ureteral disease characterized by backward flow of urine from the urinary bladder into the ureter.
